# Generated data and artifacts.
# data/chip_production.db IS committed so a hosted deploy has data on
# first boot (it is deterministic from seed=42, ~12 MB, regenerable
# any time via `python data/generate_data.py && python data/setup_database.py`).
# The CSV and the SQLite journal are still ignored.
